      • earthScroll

        protected void earthScroll(javafx.scene.input.MouseEvent event)
        Based on anchors that have been set when intially click, start rotating. Inside method there is a variable called scale. Adjusting this double value will cause the rotation to be slower or faster. 1 = normal speed, less than 1 means slower, and greater than 1 means faster.
        Parameters:
        event - Event should contain x and y of scene.
